page1.content: About Us . Derek Sol (Frontend/Basketball): Is a 17-year old senior at Del Norte High School. His favorite food is tacos. His favorite basketball team is the Pheonix Suns and his favorite player is Devin Booker. | Dillon Lee (Scrum Master/Soccer): 16 y/o junior at Del Norte High School.
